Values.value: select distinct t1.* from WMSCHEMA.WM_SAP_HR_TAO t1, WMSCHEMA.WM_FEED_EE_DELTA t3 where ((t1.EMPLID NOT IN (select t2.EMPLID from WMSCHEMA.WM_FEED_EE_DELTA t2 where trim(t2.WM_FEED_NAME)= '%targetName%')) or (t1.EMPLID=t3.EMPLID and t3.EMPLID is NOT NULL and ((to_char(t1.LASTUPDDTTM, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')>=to_char(t3.LAST_DELIVERED_DTTM, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) or (t3.STATUS!='S')) and trim(t3.WM_FEED_NAME)='%targetName%'))
